        Parameters:
        appointmentTitle - The title of the appointment.
        appointmentDescription - The description of the appointment.
        appointmentLocation - The location of the appointment.
        appointmentType - The type of appointment being scheduled.
        appointmentStart - The start time of the appointment.
        appointmentEnd - The end time of the appointment.
        customerId - The customer id associated with the appointment.
